<p>Reaper has quite a routing system. It can allow for some exceptionally cool routing configurations that will leave you scratching your head the next day.</p>

<p>In this post I’ll be going over <em>some</em> of the things you can do with Reaper’s routing, and I will also discuss why it will immolate your soul and leave nothing but the charred remains to remind you of your sins.</p>

